  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a donabe vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and coriander seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds.",
    "Add the grated ginger and minced garlic and saute until fragrant.",
    "Add the thinly sliced onion and saute until it is translucent.",
    "Add the fresh spinach and cook until it is wilted.",
    "Add the turmeric, salt, and lemon juice, and stir well.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for a few minutes.",
    "Serve the spinach dabo hot, garnished with lemon wedges."
